'''星裂菌纲'''（[[学名|学名]]：Arthoniomycetes）是[[子囊菌门|子囊菌门]][[盘菌亚门|盘菌亚门]]下的一纲。本纲仅包含了[[星裂菌目|星裂菌目]]（Arthoniales）一个目。这一纲的[[真菌|真菌]]大多是[[热带|热带]]与[[亚热带|亚热带]]的[[地衣|地衣]]。

[[系统发生学|系统发生学]]分析表明本纲是一个[[单系群|单系群]]<ref name="pmid17486977">{{cite journal |author=Spatafora JW, Sung GH, Johnson D, ''et al.'' |title=A five-gene phylogeny of Pezizomycotina |journal=[[Mycologia|Mycologia]] |volume=98 |issue=6 |pages=1018–28 |year=2006 |pmid=17486977 |doi= 10.3852/mycologia.98.6.1018|url=}}</ref>，为[[座囊菌纲|座囊菌纲]]（Dothideomycetes）的近亲。<ref name="pmid15683926">{{cite journal |author=Lumbsch HT, Schmitt I, Lindemuth R, ''et al.'' |title=Performance of four ribosomal DNA regions to infer higher-level phylogenetic relationships of inoperculate euascomycetes (Leotiomyceta) |journal=[[Mol._Phylogenet._Evol.|Mol. Phylogenet. Evol.]] |volume=34 |issue=3 |pages=512–24 |pmid=15683926 |doi=10.1016/j.ympev.2004.11.007 |url=http://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1055-7903(04)00341-0 |date=March 2005 |access-date=2011-08-06 |archive-date=2021-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210315143256/https://linkinghub.elsevier.com/retrieve/pii/S1055-7903%2804%2900341-0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

